{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2020-01-15-bash-or-zsh-log-commands.markdown/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<!-- vim-markdown-toc Redcarpet -->\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%E5%89%8D%E8%A8%80\">前言</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C\">操作</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86\">原理</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93\">总结</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#reference\">Reference</a></li>\n</ul>\n<!-- vim-markdown-toc -->\n<h1 id=\"前言\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%89%8D%E8%A8%80\" aria-label=\"前言 permalink\" class=\"toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>前言</h1>\n<p>在推上看到一篇文章<a href=\"http://18pct.com/sending-bash-and-zsh-commands-to-syslog/\">sending bash and zsh commands to syslog</a>，遂动手实践下，发现有点问题，特此记录。</p>\n<h1 id=\"操作\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C\" aria-label=\"操作 permalink\" class=\"toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>操作</h1>\n<p>1、在/etc/rsyslog.d 文件夹下，新建 commands.conf，内容如下</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"conf\"><pre class=\"language-conf\"><code class=\"language-conf\">local6.*    /var/log/commands.log</code></pre></div>\n<p>2、重启 rsyslog，<code class=\"language-text\">systemctl restart rsyslog</code></p>\n<p>3、创建/var/log/commands.log</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">touch /var/log/commands.log</code></p>\n<p>4、添加日志发送命令到对应文件</p>\n<p>.bashrc 或/etc/bashrc</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"conf\"><pre class=\"language-conf\"><code class=\"language-conf\">export PROMPT_COMMAND=&#39;RETRN_VAL=$?;logger -p local6.debug &quot;$(whoami) [$$]: $(history 1 | sed &quot;s/^[ ]*[0-9]\\+[ ]*//&quot; ) [$RETRN_VAL]&quot;&#39;</code></pre></div>\n<p>.zshrc 或/etc/bashrc</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"conf\"><pre class=\"language-conf\"><code class=\"language-conf\">precmd() { eval &#39;RETRN_VAL=$?;logger -p local6.debug &quot;$(whoami) [$$]: $(history | tail -n1 | sed &quot;s/^[ ]*[0-9]\\+[ ]*//&quot; ) [$RETRN_VAL]&quot;&#39; }\n</code></pre></div>\n<h1 id=\"原理\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86\" aria-label=\"原理 permalink\" class=\"toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>原理</h1>\n<p>通过 bash 的<a href=\"http://www.tldp.org/HOWTO/Bash-Prompt-HOWTO/x264.html\">PROMPT_COMMAND</a>和 zsh 的<a href=\"http://zsh.sourceforge.net/Doc/Release/Functions.html\">precmd</a>，在 shell 输入命令时，执行 logger 命令，将信息发送给 local6(用户自定义消息)，然后通过 commands.conf 的配置，把消息发送到/var/log/commands.log</p>\n<h1 id=\"总结\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93\" aria-label=\"总结 permalink\" class=\"toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>总结</h1>\n<p>这样就可以无感的记录操作历史了</p>\n<h1 id=\"reference\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#reference\" aria-label=\"reference permalink\" class=\"toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Reference</h1>\n<p>1、<a href=\"http://18pct.com/sending-bash-and-zsh-commands-to-syslog/\">http://18pct.com/sending-bash-and-zsh-commands-to-syslog/</a></p>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%E5%89%8D%E8%A8%80\">前言</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C\">操作</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86\">原理</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93\">总结</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#reference\">Reference</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"bash、zsh记录shell命令","date":"2020-01-15"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2020-01-15-bash-or-zsh-log-commands.markdown"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3649515864"],"slicesMap":{}}